hem and - you know, they used to - sort of thing, and - and - but we were never any trouble to our parents you see, and of course we were never allowed to play in the streets, I mean, that was unheard of, I mean that wasn't a thing you did in those days. 
You see -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15033865 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2569466\charrsid1069857 Did you have a back garden or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14232920 AH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2569466\charrsid1069857 
We had a garden, yes, we always had - you see, we always had a house you see. In those days it was - it was comparatively easy to get a house if you paid your rent you see. And - as - as I say yo
u had - you had your bit of garden. I mean, people say nowadays, oh however did they manage, they never had a bathroom and you never had these - sort of amenities you know, and you never had this that and the other, well you didn't, but then - I don't kno
w
 - I - I don't know that we wanted them in a way, I mean what you don't have you don't miss. And I - I think although I mean we weren't - you know - we - we - there was always something to do with children, I mean, you know, you always seem to be - doing 
s
omething or other, but - I think we were happier you know, we made our own - and you see we always had a - what we called a front room or a parlour in those days, and we always had a piano. You see. So that - you see, we - we used to make quite a lot of -
 our own amusements you see. And - well -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15033865 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2569466\charrsid1069857 Did everybody play the piano?
