\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15033865 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2569466\charrsid1069857 Where would you do the shopping, around the Knightsbridge area?
