Oh no, they weren't expected to. You see, that was - that was the old - which I think was rather a shame, because that was the old tradition, boys weren't supposed to do anything you see. It
 was always the girls you see, it was the girls of the of the family, that's why - it - it could have been very hard for - when you were the eldest and you were a girl, you see, because - you were just expected - oh no, the boys weren't expected to do any
thing.
