}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2569466\charrsid1069857 have}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid721979\charrsid1069857 -}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2569466\charrsid1069857 you you see, that was - you know, that was it. But -
