t - the eldest person in the - eldest one in the family be it boy or girl, wasn't it, that - that - that did the job you see, you didn't have babysitters you see, and at such times as - you know, there was a funeral on or anything and the family went, whe
re your mother and father both had to go well then of course you - you know - you fell in the gap you know, that's about the only the day that I had - took off from school or anything like that was - you know, to - to be there for that reason you see.

