 she was in - like very big choirs and that sort of thing, so of course - and of course my father wasn't at all musical, but they never quarre}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid721979\charrsid1069857 l}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
