\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15033865 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2569466\charrsid1069857 I suppose you'd be the link if your father wasn't sure what hours he was working and your mother wan't sure what she'd be doing?
