vate you know conjured up money to me you see, and of course I'd never heard of panel, I didn't know what it meant then you see, so I said, I don't think she's panel. I said, I think she must be public. So of course when the doctor came you see - so - 'co
s
 he came, so he says - oh hello, he said to mother. And - so he said, I've come to see the public patient, you see. So mother said, what? So he said, yes, he said, he said, I roared when the receptionist told me he said, he said, I knew it was Freda - 'co
s
