other ever went into hospital. You see, it was what they called a breach birth you see which - of course was very difficult, and they - they - they found it - they - they worried her because they said - she'd have to have two doctors you see and of course
 the thought of two doctors in those days was - was a - terrible expense, so she said, oh I can't afford - so one of the ladies that she knew when she heard about it - she - she gave her a letter, she was a Governor or something - at the - Westminst}{
