\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15033865 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2569466\charrsid1069857 There were lots of things going on then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14232920 AH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2569466\charrsid1069857 
Oh yes, lots of things going on, oh yes, there - there - there were really, but of course you see, as a - as child I mean you think, oh well - you know, it's - it's nice to get off to school, 'cos the same as - when we - when we used to have natu
ral history lessons you see, we were really very lucky at our little school, because they used to take us to the natural history museum you see, I mean, if it was - if it was - on butterflies and - and things like that, well - I mean the ordinary - ordina
r
y class I mean, the - the - the most they could get you would be books about it, but there, you see, you got drawers and drawers of every type of, you know, and of course as I knew the natural history museum like the back of me hand, having gone there as 
a
 small child and taken the children there on wet days and what have you I knew the places better than the teachers you see so - I'm afraid, once or twice - I and one or two of the older girls, used to give the teachers the slip because - we knew where we 
c
ould find them you see and we used to clear off on our own. I don't know what we - what we got out of it but - you know, we - we could always go there and - and - and bring the trays of butterflies - but the only thing is, now they - they used to; try and
 - do us out of that you see, when we got back to school - we used to have to write an essay - on what we did, you see. And -
