\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15033865 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2569466\charrsid1069857 And you wouldn't be able to do that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14232920 AH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2569466\charrsid1069857 Oh - oh well I did, I - because I mean I knew fairly well, you know, what was goin
g on, and then - once now and again the highlights of - of a our - our life was I think it was some lady that was connected with the school, she had a coach - sent for us and we did a tour of the cottages, Oxford and Cambridge. Well of course the same thi
n
g applied, we had to - write an essay when we got back, and of course I - I never - I never had any difficulty in writing an essay, you see, and I used to sort of try and memorize it in - always remember all the various colleges you know, I mean, didn't r
e
member them all by name but - I remember something about them, and I used to put this down and then of course this was all read out to the class and then - whoever had organised this used to all - well that was very good, well then there used to be a priz
e
s allotted you see, which I generally won, for - for that you know. That - that - that was my - sort of strong point, but I wasn't very hot on - arithmetic as I say, and - and wasn't very good at needle - well - really wasn't very good at any - oh I liked
 history, history was another strong point of mine, I was pretty good on history, not too bad on geography.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15033865 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2569466\charrsid1069857 Did you have good teachers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14232920 AH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2569466\charrsid1069857 Well - yes, they're very old teachers you know, well - I mean, to us children they were old, they were in thei
r - fifties most of them you know. You didn't have many - many young teachers in those days. But then - you see, they had a lot to do you see, they had big classes, there would only be - there was the headmistress and there'd only be - at the most - four 
t
eachers you see to take all the various classes you see so they used to have to overlap - you know, used to have history and what have you in the morning, then in the afternoon it would be - needlework and - perhaps painting you know, when - when we could
,
 you know - when - but you see they - they were considered - painting wasn't considered - a necessity the same as - history or geography was you see, it was a - you know, that was more for the - you know the - other schools, you know, to take on, you know
, that wasn't reckoned to be very much good to any of us you know.
