Oh they were - I suppose they were all right you know, they - they could be very strict, well they were rather strict in those days really you know, but what I used to have, if - if you di
d anything wrong you know - and - they used to sort of stand you up you see and then they'd say - you know, well, have to punish you, you see, and you'd think to yourself, oh well all right, I'll get a wallop you know on the hand you know and that sort of
 
thing. No. No, I won't cane you, you can write five hundred lines, well that used to annoy me more than anything, I'd much rather have had - a cut you know, a - a - than - than stay in afterwards and write five hundred lines, which I thought was a - was a
