l
though of course as I say, the majority of - of working class - the women didn't go out to work in those days, but of course it may have been a case where the father couldn't - hadn't got any work you see, and - you know, it was - well better for the chil
dren to have a - a - on meal at school anyway you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15033865 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2569466\charrsid1069857 You know people divide society into different groups?
