ow, and - for some reason or other ours were always very popular. Very popular. So that - you know, our - our parties were the things - although of course they - you know, they had to be composed of - yes, and - you know, but you - you see you - you had t
o
 think about it you see, I used to think about it two or three - days before it started you see and - get it ready, whereas the other poor woman probably you know, probably thought, oh - it's Jimmy's birthday or something today, oh well, I'll have to - do
 something you know and - and -
