Oh yes. Yes, you had birthdays cards. And of course Easter was - was quite a - quite a nice time. You know, for - for children, yes. Oh yes. Yes, we used to have Easter and Easter eggs and things -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15033865 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2569466\charrsid1069857 Chocolate bunnies and things?
\par 
