Oh yes, quite a lot of Christmas cards, oh yes, yes. Yes, of course Christmas - you know, like everything else was - was - was - very cheap, and - oh yes, we thought it was the thing to do, oh yes, we used to write to ou
r - friends and - what have you you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15033865 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2569466\charrsid1069857 Would you get many relatives round during the rest of the year, apart from Christmas?
