Oh well I - well, I mean - until I was about - four I suppose I mean - I suppose my mother used to put me to bed, or dad if he was there, oh yes, he'd do it quite as well. But -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15033865 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2569466\charrsid1069857 Did your father help to bath you and things like that do you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14232920 AH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2569466\charrsid1069857 
He would have done if he was there but he was very seldom there at that time and of course - latterly as I say - I mostly took it on, I - I - I think I did it much more than mother ever did you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15033865 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2569466\charrsid1069857 What would be their attitude if they were talking with grown ups?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14232920 AH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2569466\charrsid1069857 Oh - oh we weren't - we weren't allowed to - we weren't allowed to - to - chip in or - well we weren't very often there. You know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15033865 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2569466\charrsid1069857 What about swearing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14232920 AH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2569466\charrsid1069857 No. No, very rarely. I remember 
once - my father - trying his hands at mending some boots you know - and of course - hit himself you know, and he - yelled out, and my mother come out and she - gracious, she said, the children'll hear you, you the children'll hear you, but - no, I think 
-
 there may have been an occasional damn but I think it was - it was quite a long time before I - I knew swear words as such, and I think I mostly picked those up from other children, if you know what I mean. And - and I really - and - and of course it - i
t
 - it appals me nowadays because - it seems to come - it seems to come out into the ordinary conversation. With - with quite a lot of people. I - I don't think they realize what it is but - I think it's terrible. I think it's terrible. I think it's terrib
le. Oh no, no, my mother was very - very particular you know as children you know you say, oh ain't it, or something like that, or you go to say it you know, so mother used to say, isn't it. And - you know -
