she was a lady's maid earlier of course was all - by sea. Anyway, mum used to fly you see of course and go with her, you see, and I'd get a card perhaps one week that she'd be perhaps in the South of France or Italy or somewhere like that, the next one I'
d get through she'd be - she'd be in - in Egypt, you see, and you get - you get - thing of the Phara}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15597842\charrsid1069857 o}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2569466\charrsid1069857 
hs or something like that you see and - then all of a sudden you get, you know, something else. Well then of course not only - not only did mother have go -
 have to sort of look after her in every way, and - and that sort of thing, although they went to very good hotels where they could probably speak quite a bit of English, but at the same time - mother used to have to - have to cope with all the currency. 
